      "span_text": "The reliability of the asymptotic standard error estimates resulting from the fitting procedure rests on the Gaussian distribution of the two parameters, ascertained by the Kolmogorov-Smirnov test for continuous data applied on the result of a Monte Carlo simulation on Eq. (2) (cfr.)"
